title: Thanksgiving Preview; Hott Butt Power Rankings, & The Weakest Link Recap
itunes:title: Thanksgiving Preview; Hott Butt Power Rankings, & The Weakest Link Recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal and Colleen Wolfe recap the Monday Night Football matchup between the Bucs and Rams (4:05) The heroes preview all three of the Thanksgiving games (14:30) before going through the Ole' Zueser's Hott Butt rankings (35:33). As promised, a full weakest link recap with some special guests. (46:35)
